column9: An urban love story set in the center of Bangkok where 30-year-old Mei Li is struggling to find true love. When Mei Li accidentally meets a handsome BTS engineer whom she considers the right man, she plans to make her first move. Though too many obstacles keep popping up, Mei Li will never give up.
column12: Sirin Horwang, Theeradej Wongpuapan, Ungsumalynn Sirapatsakmetha
